<p>-Aura Points are non-transferable and may be redeemed solely for purchases made on the Vastraaura website. Aura Points hold no cash value, are not refundable, and cannot be exchanged, converted, or redeemed for cash under any circumstances</p>
<h3>Return Policy</h3>
<p>-Returns will only be considered if a return request is submitted via email within 24 hours of delivery. The request must include a detailed description of the issue along with clear images of the product. All returns are subject to review and approval by the company, and only approved requests will be eligible for return processing.</p>
<p>1. Eligibility for Return-
Products must be unused, unwashed, and in their original condition with all tags and packaging intact. The Company reserves the right to reject returns that do not meet these conditions.</p>
<p>2. Return Shipping Responsibility-
The responsibility for return shipping costs shall be borne by the customer unless otherwise stated by the Company.</p>
<h3>Approval Rights</h3>
<p>-The Company reserves the sole and absolute right to accept or reject any return request at its discretion, based on the condition of the product and the reason provided by the customer. In the event a return is approved, the Company may, at its discretion, offer a replacement product or issue Aura Points, which can be used for future purchases on the Vastraaura website. </p>
<h3>Cancellation policy</h3>
<p>-Once an order has been successfully placed and confirmed, it shall be considered final and binding. The Company does not permit cancellations after the order has been placed. Customers are therefore advised to carefully review all order details, including product specifications, quantity, and delivery information, before completing the purchase. Any requests for cancellation made after order confirmation will not be entertained under any circumstances.</p>
<h3>Pricing & Errors</h3>
